<p>At the end of the workout, you’ll find a burner exercise, which helps to exhaust the muscles for <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6950543/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">maximum hypertrophy</a>.</p>



